11#include "modules/audio_coding/codecs/pcm16b/pcm16b_common.h"
12
13#include <stdint.h>
14
15#include <initializer_list>
16
17namespace webrtc {
18
19void Pcm16BAppendSupportedCodecSpecs(std::vector<AudioCodecSpec>* specs) {
20 for (uint8_t num_channels : {1, 2}) {
21 for (int sample_rate_hz : {8000, 16000, 32000}) {
22 specs->push_back(
23 {{"L16", sample_rate_hz, num_channels},
24 {sample_rate_hz, num_channels, sample_rate_hz * num_channels * 16}});
25 }
26 }
27}
28
29} // namespace webrtc
